Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.38,0:00:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了消除汤浅高中发生的怪异现象
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.75,0:00:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和尚他们开始除灵了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.47,0:00:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但似乎完全没有作用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.01,0:00:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙在诅咒我！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.50,0:00:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.58,0:00:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事态越来越严重
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.93,0:00:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人一次都没有看我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.82,0:00:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都只盯着小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.41,0:00:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是“咒诅”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.11,0:00:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人对这个学校的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.32,0:00:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用了魇魅的法术
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.25,0:00:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让恶灵去被诅咒者那里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.25,0:00:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然真砂子和绫子都说犯人是笠井
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.09,0:00:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我却不这样认为
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.42,0:00:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.52,0:00:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像小恋推测的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.63,0:00:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在事件的相关地点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.95,0:00:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了为了咒诅而使用的人形
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.59,0:00:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在我们认为 接下来只要找到制作这些的犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.68,0:00:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事件就能够解决的时候...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.01,0:02:32.95,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,档案 3    {\r}{\u1}{\fs40}下课后的诅咒者{\r}  {\fs35}#3
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.85,0:02:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.55,0:02:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.53,0:02:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像又出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.94,0:02:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和吉野老师那时的情况一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.11,0:02:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是诅咒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.59,0:02:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错的 肯定是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.75,0:02:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是笠井千秋干的！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.14,0:02:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.67,0:03:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.86,0:03:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也要小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点抓住那个笠井不是好一点么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话我们的生命也会...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.46,0:03:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.63,0:03:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笠井不是犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还这样说么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你说其他还有谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.37,0:03:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.98,0:03:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管犯人是谁 这是警告
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.02,0:03:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和原小姐被盯上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.19,0:03:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是犯人给出的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“不要再插手这件事”的信息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.38,0:03:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么信息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.81,0:03:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真砂子是从楼梯上被推下来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.27,0:03:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋也是...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,0:03:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.08,0:03:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我想示恩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:04:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候如果我没有闯进来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不知道会变成什么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算犯人认为 最后把我们害死也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然他的目标只是为了警告而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.21,0:04:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那里入手调查事件的真相就很困难了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.70,0:04:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人的目的是吉野老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一个接一个地卷入电车事故的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.66,0:04:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐了2年5班座位的学生们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.22,0:04:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有田径部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.81,0:04:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上在出问题的座位和田径部都找出了人形
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.44,0:04:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人针对这些相关者的行动是很明显的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.14,0:04:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会遇险也是早有心理准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让事件不再恶化下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.24,0:04:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作要继续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.37,0:04:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 林和麻衣调查座位和田径部的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.70,0:04:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和尚和松崎继续在校内查找人形
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.59,0:04:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.69,0:04:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果我们就是体力劳动么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得我们对他言听计从啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.34,0:05:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 指甲都裂开了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.00,0:05:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么赔我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.36,0:05:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.04,0:05:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长头发...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.02,0:05:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是麻衣她们说的那个笠井呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.59,0:05:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个座位和田径部的交集啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最开始坐在那个座位上的是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.49,0:05:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一学期的忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.16,0:05:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二学期开始是村山同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从何时开始到何时结束的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.09,0:05:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初的换座是9月中旬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.93,0:05:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们学校每个月15日换座位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.81,0:05:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以加上暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.90,0:05:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是7月15日到9月14日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:05:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她出事故是什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.39,0:06:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换座位前的两三天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.87,0:06:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 犯人就是7月15日到9月11或12日之间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把人形藏在桌子里的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.88,0:06:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人形？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.32,0:06:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事件开始发生是在9月中旬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.95,0:06:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该和村山之前的人没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为她在这期间做了让犯人憎恨的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎恨？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.00,0:06:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她憎恨到做出那种事的地步的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.44,0:06:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人应该认识村山 哪怕只是相貌也好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.89,0:06:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.24,0:06:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是班主任的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.41,0:06:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他班的同学的嫌疑就能排除了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.24,0:06:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了联络什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.30,0:06:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有不认识的老师过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.29,0:06:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了社团的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.11,0:06:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有其他学年的人来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.37,0:06:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村山同学也是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.52,0:06:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笠井恐慌的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.05,0:07:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们好几次在教室围着笠井
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看她扭弯汤匙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候 村山同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.39,0:07:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.52,0:07:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直这么吵吵闹闹的 烦死人了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信什么超能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.11,0:07:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一群傻瓜！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.98,0:07:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅如此 村山同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还去向产砂老师抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向产砂老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.87,0:07:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,产砂老师对超能力非常了解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.73,0:07:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前也去听过几次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照分类
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扭弯汤匙是属于PKST
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.61,0:07:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 还有被称为PKMT的 对运动物体起作用的念力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.67,0:07:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.56,0:07:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔下骰子 想要扔出来二就真的出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.05,0:07:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是大部分人潜在具有的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:08:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以即使超能力事件在学校造成了大骚动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也一直保护着笠井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.20,0:08:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村山对这样的产砂老师说了抱怨的话吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.41,0:08:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说老师说了多余的话 这是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那之后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.42,0:08:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的老师 PTA都开始行动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.42,0:08:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs25}【PTA：Parent-Teacher Association 家长教师协会】
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 村山是最初否定超能力的人么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说起来 田径部也是否定派的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为顾问是那个吉野老师哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.64,0:08:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那儿的成员也都是不相信什么超能力的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.76,0:08:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实如高桥所说 反笠井派的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.58,0:08:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次都受害了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 这说明...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.32,0:08:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笠井是犯人的可能性提高了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.82,0:09:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.86,0:09:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咒诅不是什么人做都能成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.09,0:09:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有超能力的素养
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.32,0:09:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是经过了特别的修行的人才能用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.41,0:09:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.51,0:09:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋不是说了笠井同学的超能力不安定么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.17,0:09:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.17,0:09:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样不安定的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.94,0:09:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得她能使用咒诅么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.06,0:09:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.80,0:09:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咒诅是阴阳道的法术吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以阴阳师能破除咒诅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.20,0:09:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么 那个人是阴阳师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.06,0:09:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了小恋是阴阳师之后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.58,0:09:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笠井露出了惊恐的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.33,0:09:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是阴阳师？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么那样说？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.99,0:09:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.05,0:09:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.21,0:09:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.74,0:09:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 上次的事件你不是做了人形么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.26,0:09:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和尚说了 不是阴阳师的话就做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.23,0:09:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是林做的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说 林是阴阳师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.96,0:10:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.99,0:10:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.26,0:10:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笠井是犯人的可能性 还是提高了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.72,0:10:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果理解为她误以为我是阴阳师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.39,0:10:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕咒诅被打破而做的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.75,0:10:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是假设一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会她连自己都不知道 无意识地...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.61,0:10:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.53,0:10:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魇魅是积极地诅咒对方的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.66,0:10:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.03,0:10:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.07,0:10:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笠井不是会做那种事的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.18,0:10:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是麻衣的直觉么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.56,0:10:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笠井同学不是犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.56,0:10:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.93,0:10:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再相信麻衣一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.73,0:10:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去查东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:10:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣帮着大家找人形吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.11,0:11:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.47,0:11:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最开始误会的是和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.12,0:11:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到他制造人形来净灵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.29,0:11:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有识破这次的咒诅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.40,0:11:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是当然会认为他是阴阳师的么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上好像林是阴阳师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 怎么觉得被骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.28,0:11:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还以为他是阴阳师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.48,0:11:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,采取那种傲慢的态度也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.61,0:11:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才一直忍耐的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.04,0:11:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,产砂老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.27,0:11:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.52,0:11:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说原真砂子小姐受伤了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.87,0:11:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.67,0:11:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从楼梯上摔下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.37,0:11:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.28,0:11:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所幸性命没有大碍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.79,0:11:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果撞到致命的部位 就不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.12,0:12:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其现在担心 不如看好你罩着的超能力少女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.56,0:12:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 你们也认为是笠井的错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.74,0:12:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能肯定绝对不是她么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她现在很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去不知道会做出什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.86,0:12:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她会自杀什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.78,0:12:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前还来探察我们的情况呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.55,0:12:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是为了找下一个诅咒的对象么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.88,0:12:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.61,0:12:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不那么想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.50,0:12:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确切地说 我没办法那么想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.42,0:12:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不敢相信笠井是犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.14,0:12:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我也搞不清楚为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是能感觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.57,0:12:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉到？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心里有个声音在说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.57,0:12:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笠井同学不是犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.32,0:12:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只能说是一种直觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.06,0:13:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我想相信那个直觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.66,0:13:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.37,0:13:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.02,0:13:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谷山麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 谷山
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.17,0:13:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笠井也一定会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.07,0:13:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.81,0:13:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想让你说服一下其他的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.85,0:13:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想他们再逼笠井了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.77,0:13:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么说服其他人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是发生更严重的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.64,0:13:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她打算怎么担起责任啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.30,0:13:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面说不定就轮到我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.71,0:13:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.63,0:13:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之能看到的地方都找过了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.41,0:13:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.43,0:14:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在么 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.14,0:14:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.40,0:14:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.64,0:14:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.65,0:14:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐现在就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.06,0:14:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.33,0:14:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个小孩子掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.25,0:14:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:14:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.17,0:14:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那儿有书包
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.20,0:15:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书包...不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.35,0:15:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.27,0:15:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.94,0:15:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来 把脚踩到梯子上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.07,0:15:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要掉下去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.30,0:15:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次的调查也掉到井里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.59,0:15:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么老是我碰到这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.19,0:15:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.87,0:15:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋也掉下来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能松手的话就不会掉下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.32,0:16:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.99,0:16:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到梯子会...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.07,0:16:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.09,0:16:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就会有人来救我们的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.85,0:16:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟别人说了要来这儿么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.42,0:16:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.62,0:16:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 有人么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.64,0:16:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么来这儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.65,0:16:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我听到小孩子的哭声
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.80,0:16:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后找了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现这里面有个女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.86,0:16:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.23,0:16:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.39,0:16:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我没觉得奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.52,0:16:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边一片黑暗什么都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.78,0:16:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有那个孩子看得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.87,0:16:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于麻衣也被盯上了么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么能那么镇定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.48,0:16:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.97,0:16:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且马上就要天黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.02,0:16:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.07,0:16:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人 那个小孩再出现的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.51,0:16:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更惨的是 我竟然和最冷漠的人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说把他拖下来是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.18,0:17:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.70,0:17:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是该鼓励我安慰我的么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.87,0:17:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细想想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.87,0:17:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是...二人世界～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.98,0:17:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复活了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.78,0:17:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚他的表情很像我梦里的小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.29,0:17:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得出我复活了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.03,0:17:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得出
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.47,0:17:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣先会沮丧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后会生气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就会恢复心情 一往直前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.62,0:17:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能这么清楚的知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.87,0:17:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你的心情都写在脸上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.00,0:17:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的啊 哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.67,0:17:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.71,0:17:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来介绍我的宠物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.01,0:17:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会是那个500元的硬币吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.62,0:17:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你小看它 它躲起来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.83,0:17:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人 明明在小恋手里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.86,0:18:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.75,0:18:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.79,0:18:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.18,0:18:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.46,0:18:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.62,0:18:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 没有扔给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.50,0:18:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为麻衣声音太大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.16,0:18:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它害怕地躲起来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.17,0:18:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁声音太大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.60,0:18:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.57,0:18:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你变的魔术真高明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.17,0:18:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得是魔术么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.98,0:18:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.59,0:18:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说 说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.24,0:18:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是害怕麻衣么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.32,0:18:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.32,0:18:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.14,0:18:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为麻衣不是像外表看上去那样可怕的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.63,0:18:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.76,0:18:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.36,0:18:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就是腹语术吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.75,0:18:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.20,0:18:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但看上去就像是硬币真的在说话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.59,0:18:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.79,0:18:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多玩一些什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.69,0:18:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不能再做更复杂的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.67,0:19:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么地方受伤了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没带道具
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.75,0:19:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是黑暗的缘故么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.60,0:19:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋看起来脸色不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,且不说其他的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家集合后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.77,0:19:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有出现的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.90,0:19:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少小林会...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.20,0:19:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管发生什么都不要离开我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.03,0:19:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.62,0:19:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.66,0:19:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.92,0:19:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西不是一天两天就能成长起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.05,0:19:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要惊慌失措而自取灭亡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.10,0:19:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.22,0:20:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.66,0:20:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.54,0:20:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...谁来...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.34,0:20:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和尚 绫子 谁都好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.40,0:20:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.52,0:20:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.88,0:20:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么突然...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋 在么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.90,0:20:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动作真快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.69,0:20:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我们绳索或梯子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.35,0:20:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有手电筒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.33,0:20:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然做了这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过下水道还真是盲点阿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.35,0:21:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣 我和原小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.28,0:21:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有吉野老师的人偶都有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.09,0:21:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有我们的名字么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.36,0:21:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像松了一口气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像被人无视了的感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来只要把这些人偶随水冲掉或者烧掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.65,0:21:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魇魅的力量就能消除了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.87,0:21:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样犯人就会停手么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.29,0:21:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最关键的犯人又不知道是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.52,0:21:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先说好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.63,0:21:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是笠井的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.36,0:21:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.02,0:21:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.68,0:21:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不舒服么？小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.56,0:21:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.09,0:22:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.54,0:23:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 档案3
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.70,0:23:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下课后的诅咒者  第四章
